Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,阿……阿阿阿阿…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬 接棒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,事出无奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,允许您使用龙枪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:48.19,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalalalalalala
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:52.90,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalalalalala
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:55.28,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}やあ また会えた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:56.66,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}ねぇ こんばんは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.57,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}いや こんにちはだって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:01.12,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}広いようで 狭いようで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:03.83,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}退屈はいらないみたいだね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:06.71,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}あぁ 問題は依然あって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:08.75,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}頭痛いんだけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:11.17,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}少しずつって言い聞かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:14.34,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}願い事叶えて行きましょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:18.39,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}I shall remember I wanna do I shall remember
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:24.23,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}拾い集めた後悔のかけらたちを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:26.48,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}夜が明ける前に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:30.48,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}何遍を貼って 並べてて 希望に変える
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:33.03,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}10秒継続中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:37.03,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}桜が去つて散ったその後で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:40.83,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}何が真実なのかは かるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:44.66,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}future melody そう今は奏でて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:49.58,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}愛が世界救うのだなんて 僕は信じてないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:55.26,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}今 目の前の君が 明日を生きれるくらいには
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:56.55,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}ありえない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:59.05,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不条理は吹き飛ばしていけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:00.34,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}with 喜怒哀楽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:03.81,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}大丈夫さ　どこまでもゆくだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:09.27,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalala　lalalalalala!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:04.05,edch,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:55.28,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}呀啊 又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:56.66,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}呐 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.57,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不 应该是中午好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:01.12,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}好像很宽敞 又好像很拥挤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:03.83,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不过貌似和「无聊」二字无缘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:06.71,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}啊 问题依然还在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:08.75,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}真是让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:11.17,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不过还是向我慢慢道来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:14.34,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}让我们一起去实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:24.23,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}将散落一地的后悔的碎片小心收起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:26.48,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在天明之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:30.48,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}一遍遍地粘合 一遍遍地重排 将之变为希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:33.03,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}持续10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:37.03,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在那满树樱花逝去之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:40.83,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}什么才是真实 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:44.66,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}future melody 没错 现在就奏响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:49.58,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}都说爱会拯救世界 我可一点都不信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:55.26,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}现在 眼前的你 想要享受明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:56.55,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:59.05,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}先把不合理统统打飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:00.34,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}with 喜怒哀乐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:03.81,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}放心吧 我们无所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,九段…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,云切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,五十段…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,月永
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,七十二段…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,波打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,终段…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,大…烟…火哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没能把龙枪运用自如啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,小姬她们市的市长森野 还有秘书篠冢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,和…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 你这是对小姬做什么啊 森野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啰…啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 本来想好好打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不过貌似有事要忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎…怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,空气…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对妖特殊广域结界…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,开启
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝 恭助 桃华
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,喔喔 这个还真有效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这结界会对妖力产生反应 对齐施加相应的负荷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对不完全是妖怪的对象貌似没什么效果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对妖?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,结界?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 阿姬 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是刚说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这东西会对妖力起反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬是…妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,把小姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,把小姬放了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是对妖力起反应的结界…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那这家伙也一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙…和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,巡夜让年轻人来不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事重在大家参与啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哼…所以咱们那精神过头的町长才…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧 菊奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,快离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不准…不准对我的市民们出手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我来对付你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢陪小丫头玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,把小姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这就放人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不过有两个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,第一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,让那孩子放弃候选人资格 选现町长连任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,森野…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,然后第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,将樱新町的町长权限交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没有商量的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,期限为今晚 我在中央大道等你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细考虑一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,振作点 阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你…竟然是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要瞒着我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,春疾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,空气变了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,结界并没有被消除哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,八重小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是削减了这座城市的妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然从结果上看是减轻了妖怪们的负荷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但并没有直接给予你们帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以老哥应该不会有意见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因为整座城市妖力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有东西将会复苏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那便是六年前我亲手封印的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,记…记忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来 你的妖力就基本被封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 八重小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这孩子妖力实在太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,伤疤…脖子上有了这么大个伤疤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(640,608)}只能用这个方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别哭哭啼啼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你将来不是要当町长的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧 我…我再去改一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不用?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 这样就很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那就这样吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,请求?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,从我当上町长那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,请从大家脑中消除我是妖怪的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得 这样一来我就能从妖怪和人类双方的视角
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来看待各种各样的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要被封印的记忆中 也包括因你是妖怪而起的所有事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,比如那条围巾的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,想起来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名从小就喜欢把所有事自己一肩承担对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我也这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因为秋名这一点…我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这次好像不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,救救小姬 救救这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好咯 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬交给我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你们去做你们能做的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是阿姬笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬笔记?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬每天都在记录城市里的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,四月十六日 大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,659)}三丁目铃木家的狗逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,名字叫约翰 发现者请尽快联络
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655}吉原奶奶感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉她如果总是治不好要去医院看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)}而丁目北山家的公寓又来了新住户
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,打招呼时要让他们注意关门窗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)}甚六爷爷今天也很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,脚貌似也好了很多 我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是春天却和夏天一样热
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,慰劳会变成了游泳大会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微闹得过火了些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不过…好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:12.46,XIAOZI,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.87\frx358\fry2\pos(453.333,638)}虽\N然\N发\N生\N了\N很\N多\N事\N\N但\N都\N平\N安\N解\N决\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,别太乱来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,此时不乱来更待何时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…大伙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再来确认一下作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:13:00.05,XIAOZI,,0,0,0,,{\fs43\move(976,134,976,90)}熊组
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:13:00.05,XIAOZI,,0,0,0,,{\fs43\move(976,296,976,252)}言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:13:00.05,XIAOZI,,0,0,0,,{\fs43\move(956,410,956,366)}蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:13:00.05,XIAOZI,,0,0,0,,{\fs43\move(976,525,976,481)}桃华
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:13:00.05,XIAOZI,,0,0,0,,{\fs43\move(996,642,996,598)}巡逻车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:05.01,XIAOZI - lan,,0,0,0,,{\fs43\pos(825.6,147)}马组
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我 蓝 桃华一组
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,先去想办法处理对妖结界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 秋明和恭助马上冲进去救出小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但到底该怎么做啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那个老头之前打了次手机是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,估计是指示别的什么家伙展开结界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 阿姬怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 刚才睡下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,已经通知市民们去公民馆避难了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们去市外不是更安全吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们往外走一步试试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,出不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,倒不如说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没有出去的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,市民们出不去也是一样的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是那个老头搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那个老爷爷到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,八重也许知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看招 看招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 已经不能指望八重了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,加油哦 BABY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 要想想下一步怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不 看来没那个必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,说好的大道应该是前面那条吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,搞错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,来投降的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看来不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么呐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都去避难了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 阿姬不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙命硬着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么 别带着了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,听好 阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以忘记哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,被人们所爱 被城市所爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,被龙所爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在还需要睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,之前被打得好惨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好惨…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,状况如何了 市民们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,都去避难了 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是…不够资格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,给市民们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,龙枪也断了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,让人们和龙都失望透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是该辞去町长一职了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,飞弹牛?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,市民们都很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,去避难所前都看望过你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,明天就是你当上町长的第七年了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,龙什么的我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:59.37,XIAOZI,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\frz353.2\move(608,542,600,604,0,5485)}祝早日康复
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但至少人们还是超喜欢阿姬的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,必须保护城市
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你还要静养
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,最少还需要一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一小时?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名他们明明正在拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你却让我等一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,相信他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,町长小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,至少为止都努力六年了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,耽误一小时而已 大家会谅解的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是孤身一人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这边这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那么那么 那边怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩不是认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不…倒是交换过名片…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,从这怪力看应该是妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他没受影响
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,既是人类又是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,基本不会受结界影响
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是曾堕化过的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,与你们的言灵使一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真是讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这家伙会在这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊 这次又是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,结界还没搞定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,现在没空管那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥你们那边也打起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,总之必须消除结界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不然咱们两边都会被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哇啊 这次是我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧 区长?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,结界让玛利亚贝尔很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要赶紧收拾掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就算您这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那给你个提示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,结界的发生源是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,发生源是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,市内某处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好广
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我够给面子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧找出来收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,找…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧 为什么是让我…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因为只有你能找到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,雄飞先生说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我能做到的事 只有我能做到的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我能做到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,只有蓝能做到的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要读取所有东京居民的内心?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,所有居民?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有1200万人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一…二…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,广域读心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝 不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,地点…地点是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,千代田区…不…是港区…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是个很高很高的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了吗 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,高处?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再具体点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再继续下去蓝就撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,市中心…高处…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里的理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,频道调不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,能让结界波大幅展开的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,东京塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:59.46,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 心爱之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:03.05,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}将时钟的指针拨反过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:04.88,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在梦中轻轻啜泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:09.68,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}我又开始了今天的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:25.24,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}喜欢谈天说地却讨厌侧耳倾听
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:28.86,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}喜欢品尝美食却讨厌亲手烹调
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:32.49,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}能包容你如此任性的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:36.20,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}全世界就只有我一人 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:39.87,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}这眼泪是为谁而流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:43.50,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}为我吗 亦或是为你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:47.22,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}流干眼泪之后又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:50.84,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}还是想和谁在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.84,0:22:54.35,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:57.98,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}听我讲述昨夜的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:01.90,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在这个破除了魔法的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:05.32,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}我四处搜寻着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:09.03,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:12.62,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}让我听一听你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:19.33,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}再次将我带入甜美的梦乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:59.46,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 爱しい人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:03.05,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}时计の针を逆さまに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:04.88,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}梦に泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:09.68,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}今日もまた 仆は生きる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:25.24,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}おしゃべりがすき 闻くのはきらい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:28.86,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}食べることがすき 作るのはきらい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:32.49,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}そんなわがままが通じるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:36.20,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}世界で仆だけと知っていたかい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:39.87,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}この涙は 谁のものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:43.50,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}仆のためか 君のためか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:47.22,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}カラカラになってそれからまた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:50.84,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}谁かといたいと思えるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.84,0:22:54.35,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 爱しい人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:57.98,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}昨日までの梦のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:01.90,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}魔法がとけたこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:05.32,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}仆は君を探したよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:09.03,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 爱しい人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:12.62,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}君の声を闻かせてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:19.33,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}梦の中でもう一度 连れていくよ
